 suggest a power law fit to opening angle versus age with an\nexponent of ~0.32 and 0.02, respectively for ages less than 8000 yr and greater\nthan 8000 yr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2013 23:12:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
