xt of initial data sets evolving by the vacuum Einstein\nevolution equation. The definition of quasi-local angular momentum provides an\nanswer to the second problem in classical general relativity on Penrose's list\n[18].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2013 23:47:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2014 04:20:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-06"}
